      "description": "PIV and hemolysis index measurements collected on FDA generic centrifugal blood pump test rig, adult-equivalent flow conditions. Validation completed November 2022. RH < 1 at all five operating points. GCI < 2% on hemolysis-weighted shear metric. Dataset predates pediatric indication expansion (Q3 2024).",
      "generatedAtTime": "2022-11-15T00:00:00Z"
