      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented build and test suite; no unresolved critical defects.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under institutional SQA plan. Version control logs and regression test suite results reviewed. No open critical defects at time of study."
    },
