      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; nominal input values documented with source references.",
      "rationale": "Fluid properties (density 1050 kg/m³, viscosity 3.5 cP), geometry dimensions, and rotational speed sourced from device master record and FDA benchmark geometry file. Input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
