      "rationale": "Blood analog (aqueous glycerol, 40% v/v) prepared per ASTM F1841. Three independent batches used across validation runs. Sample characterization records archived. Statistical sample size analysis not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
