      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD input parameters (geometry, fluid properties, boundary conditions) equivalent to physical test configuration within documented tolerances.",
      "rationale": "CAD geometry imported directly from device master record; dimensional inspection confirmed < 0.05 mm deviation from nominal. Fluid properties matched to blood analog characterization data. Rotational speed set to ±0.5 RPM of test rig encoder readings. Equivalency confirmed for adult validation configuration. Pediatric operating conditions (lower flow, adjusted speed setpoints) have not been subject to equivalency assessment as no corresponding physical test configuration exists."
